## Directory Structure Strategy (`/AI Engine`)

```text
AI Engine/
├── requirements.txt
├── main.py                     # FastAPI Entrypoint (REST routes for Java Backend)
├── worker.py                   # Temporal Worker Process
├── app/
│   ├── generators/             # System 1 & 2
│   │   ├── template_generator.py # Auto-generates Profession Templates
│   │   ├── agent_spawner.py      # Auto-generates Agent DNA & Memory
│   ├── runtime/                # System 3
│   │   ├── workflows.py          # Temporal Execution Workflows
│   │   ├── graph.py              # LangGraph ReAct Logic
│   │   ├── tools_registry.py     # Permitted Actions
│   ├── memory/                 # System 4
│   │   ├── qdrant_service.py     # strict tenant-isolated vector retrieval
│   ├── intelligence/           # System 5
│   │   ├── forecaster.py         # Evaluates supply/demand signals
│   ├── core/                   # Kafka config, Ollama config, Security
```

