## Production Execution Rules
* **No Mock Data:** Every AI generation must go through Ollama (`http://localhost:11434`). Every memory must go to Qdrant (`http://localhost:6333`). Every state change must publish to Kafka (`http://localhost:9092`).
* **Stateless Agents:** The LangGraph instances must hold zero in-memory state between crashes. Temporal handles all persistence.

